 (epic) holds aggro over the necro pet.  When in a group with a magician (non-epic) my pet (epic) holds aggro over the other pet.  When in a group with a bard or other light melee, my pet (epic) holds aggro about half the time.  When soloing, if I lead with my pet, I can sit right next to the mob and my pet (epic) will hold aggro the entire fight.<br>
